data.description: ~HORSE PROPERY~Nestled amidst the picturesque landscapes of Bear Valley Springs, this charming home boasts a generous 1918 square feet of living space. With its inviting ambiance, delightful features, and expansive 1.54-acre lot, this property offers a truly idyllic retreat.Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The spacious living area provides an ideal space for relaxation and entertaining, featuring large windows that fill the room with natural light and offer breathtaking views of the surrounding countryside.The kitchen is a culinary haven, equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient island. It's the perfect spot to whip up delicious meals and create lasting memories with loved ones.This home offers three cozy bedrooms, each providing a tranquil sanctuary for rest and rejuvenation. The master bedroom is particularly inviting, with an ensuite bathroom that offers a private oasis for relaxation.Step outside onto the expansive 1.54-acre lot, and you'll find yourself surrounded by nature's beauty. The property includes a barn, providing endless possibilities for hobbies, storage, or even transforming it into a workshop. Embrace the outdoors and take advantage of the abundant space to create your own personal oasis, whether it be a vibrant garden, a serene patio area, or even a playground for the little ones.Located in the desirable community of Bear Valley Springs, this home offers access to a range of amenities, including equestrian trails, hiking paths, tennis courts, and a community pool. Immerse yourself in the natural beauty of the area, with stunning views of rolling hills, majestic oak trees, and clear blue skies.Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and tranquility that awaits you in Bear Valley Springs.
